2006;;The Teddy Bear Master;;American;;Charlie Ours;;Isaac Imel;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Teddy_Bear_Master;;After he is embarrassed by his teacher, a student dubbed "The Teddy Bear Master" brings a group of stuffed teddy bears to life, then orders them to kill the teacher, Mr Clevenger. A group of students battle the bears in an attempt to save Clevenger, but Clevenger and his wife ultimately come to a sticky end.[1][3]